                  figcaption.tiny The Non-Designer’s Design Book, 4th ed. Robin Williams, Peachpit Press, 2015.

          section
            h2 Contrast
            .flex
              .half
                ul.small
                  li If not identical, then very different
                  li.fragment Avoid similar

              .half
